diameter	spread	The maximum distance between any two points.	population	space		$$\max_{x,y \in \mathcal{X}} \|x-y\|$$	- Insensitive to the shape of the distribution.
- Does not consider whether the agents at the boundaries are outliers or the edges of large clusters.	[Bramson et al. (2016)](https://doi.org/10.1080/0022250X.2016.1147443), [Bramson et al. (2017)](https://doi.org/10.1086/688938)
volume	spread	The volume of the minimal convex polytope that includes all points.	population	space			- Insensitive to the shape of the distribution.
- Does not consider whether the agents at the boundaries are outliers or the edges of large clusters.	[Bramson et al. (2016)](https://doi.org/10.1080/0022250X.2016.1147443), [Bramson et al. (2017)](https://doi.org/10.1086/688938)
